    <briefdescription>
<para>Class for saving information about textual layer correctness of the document chunk. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para><itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>correct - if the document chunk contains correct textual layer or not</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>start - start page of the document chunk (numeration starts with 1)</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>end - end page of the document chunk (numeration starts with 1, end included)</para>
